<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head>


<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Mochi Catto — Mini Game</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin="">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&amp;family=Nunito:wght@400;600;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #faf0e1;
    --cream-2: #f5e4cc;
    --peach: #f4c8a8;
    --peach-dark: #e89060;
    --brown: #6b4a3b;
    --brown-dark: #3d2a22;
    --accent: #e07a4f;
    --angry: #c85a5a;
    --happy: #8db96a;
    --shadow: 0 6px 0 #d9c3a4, 0 12px 24px rgba(90, 50, 20, 0.18);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 20% -10%, #ffe8cd 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 600px at 110% 110%, #fbd6bc 0%, transparent 55%),
      var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Nunito', system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
  }
  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 32px 20px;
  }
  .app {
    width: min(1120px, 100%);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 320px;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 920px) {
    .app { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .title-bar {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .title-bar h1 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .title-bar h1 .accent { color: var(--peach-dark); }
  .title-bar .sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--brown);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fffaf1;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    padding: 18px;
  }

  /* HUD */
  .hud {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .hud-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 78px;
  }
  .hud-label {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--brown);
    opacity: 0.75;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .hud-value {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .hud-value.combo { color: var(--peach-dark); }
  .hud-value.time  { color: var(--brown-dark); }
  .hud-value.time.low { color: var(--angry); }

  /* Purr meter */
  .meter-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .meter-top {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--brown);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .meter-top .mood { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
  .mood-dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--happy);
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px #fff8;
  }
  .mood-dot.neutral { background: #f4c86a; }
  .mood-dot.angry   { background: var(--angry); }
  .meter {
    height: 18px;
    background: #f2ddbf;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    image-rendering: pixelated;
  }
  .meter-fill {
    height: 100%;
    width: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--happy), #bfdb8e);
    transition: width 120ms linear, background 300ms ease;
  }
  .meter-fill.warn { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e0a040, #f4c86a); }
  .meter-fill.danger { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a83d3d, var(--angry)); }
  .meter-ticks {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
      90deg, transparent 0, transparent 9%, rgba(61,42,34,0.12) 9%, rgba(61,42,34,0.12) 10%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Canvas */
  .canvas-wrap {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffe9cf 0%, #f8d3b0 100%);
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  }
  canvas#game {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    image-rendering: pixelated;
    image-rendering: crisp-edges;
    cursor: grab;
    touch-action: none;
  }
  canvas#game.petting { cursor: grabbing; }
  canvas#game.angry   { cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* Overlay screens */
  .overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: rgba(61, 42, 34, 0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    z-index: 10;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .overlay.hidden { display: none; }
  .overlay-card {
    background: #fffaf1;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px 30px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 0 #3d2a22;
    min-width: 320px;
    max-width: 440px;
  }
  .overlay-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
  }
  .overlay-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--brown);
    margin: 6px 0;
  }
  .overlay-card .big-score {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--peach-dark);
    margin: 14px 0 6px;
  }
  .overlay-card .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: var(--cream-2);
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    margin: 8px 4px 0;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
  }

  .btn {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    background: var(--peach-dark);
    color: #fffaf1;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 0 var(--brown-dark);
    transition: transform 80ms ease, box-shadow 80ms ease;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 5px 0 var(--brown-dark); }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(3px); box-shadow: 0 1px 0 var(--brown-dark); }
  .btn.secondary {
    background: #fffaf1;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
  }

  /* Sweet spot hints */
  .spot-hints {
    display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--brown);
  }
  .chip {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: var(--cream-2);
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
  }
  .chip .dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--happy);
  }
  .chip.ears .dot { background: #c27bd0; }
  .chip.chin .dot { background: #6aa9db; }
  .chip.head .dot { background: #e0a040; }
  .chip.belly .dot { background: var(--angry); }

  /* Personal record card */
  .pr-block { text-align: center; }
  .pr-big {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--peach-dark);
    margin: 6px 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .pr-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--brown);
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .pr-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--brown);
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .pr-meta > div { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(61,42,34,0.2); padding: 2px 0; }
  .pr-new {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    background: var(--happy);
    color: #fffaf1;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* Side panel */
  .side {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px;
  }
  .panel h3 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .lb-list {
    list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
  }
  .lb-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 22px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .lb-row.me { background: #fff1d6; box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px var(--peach-dark); }
  .lb-rank {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--peach-dark);
  }
  .lb-name { font-weight: 700; }
  .lb-score {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
  }
  .lb-row .medal { color: var(--peach-dark); font-weight: 800; }

  /* Tweaks panel */
  /* Designer modal */
  .designer-modal {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(61, 42, 34, 0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    display: none;
    place-items: center;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .designer-modal.on { display: grid; }
  .designer-card {
    background: #fffaf1;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 0 #3d2a22;
    width: min(820px, 100%);
    max-height: 92vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .designer-head {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    background: var(--cream-2);
  }
  .designer-head h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
  }
  .designer-head .x { cursor: pointer; font-size: 22px; color: var(--brown); line-height: 1; }
  .designer-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .designer-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .preview-col {
    padding: 18px;
    border-right: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff5e4, #fbe5cc);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  }
  .preview-label {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  #previewCanvas {
    width: 224px; height: 187px;
    image-rendering: pixelated;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffe9cf, #f8d3b0);
  }
  .preview-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--brown);
    opacity: 0.8;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 10px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .controls-col {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    max-height: 70vh;
  }
  .ctrl-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .ctrl-group > label {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .opt-row {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;
  }
  .opt {
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--cream);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    transition: transform 60ms ease;
  }
  .opt:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .opt.active {
    background: var(--peach-dark);
    color: #fffaf1;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px var(--brown-dark);
  }
  .color-picker-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(8, 1fr); gap: 6px;
  }
  .color-pick {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
  }
  .color-pick.active::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: -3px;
    border: 2px solid var(--peach-dark);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .toggle-row {
    display: flex; gap: 10px;
  }

  .tweaks {
    position: fixed;
    right: 20px;
    bottom: 20px;
    width: 280px;
    background: #fffaf1;
    border: 3px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 0 var(--brown-dark);
    z-index: 50;
    display: none;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .tweaks.on { display: block; }
  .tweaks h4 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .tweaks h4 .x { cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; color: var(--brown); }
  .tweak-row { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .tweak-row label {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--brown);
    display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .tweak-row input[type="range"] { width: 100%; }
  .tweak-row select {
    width: 100%; padding: 6px;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .color-swatches {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 6px;
  }
  .swatch {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
  }
  .swatch.selected::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: -4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--peach-dark);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  /* Floating score popups */
  .pop {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--happy);
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: pop 800ms ease-out forwards;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #fffaf1, -2px -2px 0 #fffaf1, 2px -2px 0 #fffaf1, -2px 2px 0 #fffaf1;
    z-index: 5;
  }
  .pop.bad { color: var(--angry); }
  .pop.neutral { color: var(--brown); }
  .pop.crit { color: var(--peach-dark); font-size: 18px; }
  @keyframes pop {
    0%   { transform: translate(-50%, -10%) scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
    20%  { transform: translate(-50%, -40%) scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: translate(-50%, -120%) scale(1); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Mood banner on canvas */
  .mood-banner {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: #fffaf1;
    border: 2px solid var(--brown-dark);
    border-radius: 20px;
    color: var(--brown-dark);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 250ms ease;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 4;
  }
  .mood-banner.show { opacity: 1; }
  .mood-banner.angry { background: #c85a5a; color: #fffaf1; }
  .mood-banner.happy { background: var(--happy); color: #fffaf1; }

  /* Screen shake */
  .canvas-wrap.shake { animation: shake 260ms ease; }
  @keyframes shake {
    0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }
    25%     { transform: translate(-4px, 2px); }
    50%     { transform: translate(4px, -2px); }
    75%     { transform: translate(-2px, 3px); }
  }

  .footer-note {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--brown);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body style="cursor: crosshair; background-color: rgb(255, 228, 189); font-family: monospace;" data-cc-id="cc-1">
<div class="page">
  <div class="app" id="app">

    <div class="title-bar">
      <div>
        <h1>PET THE <span class="accent">CAT</span></h1>
        <div class="sub">Just play whenever you're bored. no need to be angry okaii!</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <button class="btn secondary" id="settingsBtn" style="margin-right:8px;">⚙️ Settings</button>
        <button class="btn secondary" id="designBtn" style="margin-right:8px;">🎨 Design Cat</button>
        <button class="btn secondary" id="howBtn">How to play</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="gameCard">
      <div class="hud">
        <div class="hud-stat">
          <span class="hud-label">SCORE</span>
          <span class="hud-value" id="scoreVal">3022</span>
        </div>
        <div class="meter-wrap">
          <div class="meter-top">
            <span>PURR METER</span>
            <span class="mood">
              <span id="moodLabel">ANGRY</span>
              <span class="mood-dot angry" id="moodDot"></span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="meter">
            <div class="meter-fill" id="meterFill" style="width: 98.8756%;"></div>
            <div class="meter-ticks"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-stat" style="text-align:right; align-items:flex-end;">
          <span class="hud-label">TIME</span>
          <span class="hud-value time low" id="timeVal">0</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="canvas-wrap shake" id="canvasWrap">
        <canvas id="game" width="640" height="480" class=""></canvas>
        <div class="mood-banner angry" id="moodBanner">ANGRY!</div>
        <div class="overlay hidden" id="startOverlay">
          <div class="overlay-card">
            <h2>Ready to pet?</h2>
            <p>Click and drag on Mochi's <b>sweet spots</b> — ears, chin, head. Keep the <b>purr meter</b> full.</p>
            <p style="opacity:0.75;">⚠️ Touch the belly or over-pet and Mochi gets <b>angry</b>. You'll lose score fast.</p>
            <button class="btn" id="startBtn">START</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay" id="endOverlay">
          <div class="overlay-card">
            <h2 id="endTitle">PURRFECT!</h2>
            <div class="big-score" id="endScore">3023</div>
            <p id="endMsg">Mochi is in love. Best pets of the week.</p>
            <div>
              <span class="tag" id="tagMax">Max combo: 30</span>
              <span class="tag" id="tagSweet">Sweet hits: 143</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; justify-content:center; margin-top: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
              <button class="btn" id="againBtn">PLAY AGAIN</button>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:11px; opacity:0.7; margin-top:10px;" id="saveHint"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay" id="howOverlay">
          <div class="overlay-card" style="text-align:left;">
            <h2 style="text-align:center;">How to play</h2>
            <p><b>Drag</b> across the cat to pet. Hitting <b>sweet spots</b> in sequence builds combos.</p>
            <p><b>Purr meter</b> decays over time. Keep it above zero or Mochi gets grumpy — score drains and hits start failing.</p>
            <p>Watch the <b>tail</b>: if it starts twitching, back off the same spot. Over-pet = <b>hiss</b> and meter crash.</p>
            <p><b>Avoid the belly</b> — it's a trap!</p>
            <div style="text-align:center;">
              <button class="btn" id="howCloseBtn">GOT IT</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="spot-hints">
        <span class="chip ears"><span class="dot"></span>EARS ×2</span>
        <span class="chip chin"><span class="dot"></span>CHIN ×1.5</span>
        <span class="chip head"><span class="dot"></span>HEAD ×1</span>
        <span class="chip belly"><span class="dot"></span>BELLY ⚠ TRAP</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="side">
      <div class="card panel">
        <h3>🏅 PERSONAL RECORD</h3>
        <div id="personalRecord" class="pr-block">
          <div class="pr-big" id="prScore">—</div>
          <div class="pr-sub" id="prSub">No runs yet — get out there and pet.</div>
          <div class="pr-meta" id="prMeta"></div>
          <button class="btn secondary" id="prResetBtn" style="font-size:9px; padding:8px 12px; margin-top:10px;">RESET RECORD</button>
        </div>
      </div>
